DOTVIM README

First stepps:

	Installation:
		
		git clone https://github.com/D1ng5/dotvim.git ~/.vim

	Simbolic links:

		ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
		ls -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

	install Submodules:
	
		cd ~/.vim
		git submodule init
		git submodule update


	add Submodules for instance pathogen
										folder of the submodule
		 git submodule add git://github.com/tpope/vim-pathogen.git autoload/pathogen
